HEADWORD: Atrocity
<hw>A*troc"i*ty</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Atrocities</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[F.
